  <steps>
    <step num="0">Preheat the oven to 190°C (375°F). </step>
    <step num="1">Place the pork in a bowl along with all the marinade ingredients. Combine and leave to marinade for 6-8 hours. </step>
    <step num="2">Place the pork belly on a grill tray. </step>
    <step num="3">Roast the pork belly in the oven for 20 minutes, turning halfway through. </step>
    <step num="4">Enjoy! </step>
